cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CY 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to classify residential requests. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves the use of unsupervised clustering algorithms, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of classifiers and neural networks also suggests the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques, which falls under the category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper deals with smart cities and digital government services, which suggests the category of cs.CY (Computers and Society).
